HDHRUtil-Tuner-channelSettingRestore - Restore the channel status from a file


usage: HDHRUtil-Tuner-channelSettingRestore [-h] --hdhr HDHR [--infile INFILE] [--use-cloud-discovery]

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --hdhr HDHR           the HDHomeRun to manage
  --infile INFILE, --input-file INFILE
                        the file from which to restore the HDHR settings
  --use-cloud-discovery
                        use the SiliconDust Cloud API services to discover local tuners



Scenario:

You want to restore the channel settings to a HDHR

   HDHRUtil-Tuner-channelSettingSave --hdhr=hdhr1.local --infile hdhr1.settings

